text: Modou Lamin Jadama (born 17 March 1994) is a Gambian footballer who currently plays as a centre back for Atlanta United 2 in the USL Championship. He made his professional debut for Colo-Colo against Santiago Wanderers in February 2015 for the Santo Tomás Cup, which his team won by penalties.
